Whatever Game
=============
About
    A gaming platform with two games; Pew Wep and 5Pad.
    This is a school project for "Datavetenskap I - Programvarukonstruktion [2011]".
Authors
    Hannes Landstedt
    Simon Landstedt
    Anders Wik
